         <abstract id="aspace_420807fcae26300f6f14ad2c193a3c4c">The papers consist of correspondence, reports, and research material almost exclusively devoted to John Boyce's work on wood and wood diseases. About a third of the papers relate to Boyce's work on the use of wood in airplanes during World War I.</abstract>
